        </div>
        <div class="cs-section">
          <div class="cs-label">Dtype</div>
          <div class="cs-row"><code>x.dtype</code><span>Returns torch.float32 etc.</span></div>
          <div class="cs-row"><code>x.float()</code><span>Cast to float32</span></div>
